  <trk>
    <name>Fearnley Grounds Walk 5</name>
    <desc>This walking session at Centennial Park may represent one of the most dynamic off-leash environments available within the Sydney metropolitan area. The route, captured in the Garmin activity log, covers the central pond system extending from Kensington Pond to Busbys Pond. This region of the park is designated as an off-leash zone, providing a controlled but unconstrained movement area suitable for observing canine locomotion patterns, environmental engagement, and behavioural responses to open-space stimuli.</desc>
    <type>running</type>
